Name: Death in the Night
About the game: Death in the Night is a game in which you have to collect the souls of cats and overcome deadly traps. Features: Gloomy atmosphere Deadly traps Saws, a lot of saws Cats (souls of cats) Levers, teleports, doors Complete the levels and get achievements. History: The main character is death collecting the souls of seals. What happened in this world? There is no answer to this question, but you can run jump and squat in a deadly puzzle platformer game.
